                            269 ;;
                            270 ;; Details:
                            271 ;;    This macro performs the subtraction of DE - A and stores it directly on DE.
                            272 ;; It uses only DE and A to perform the operation.
                            273 ;;
                            274 ;; Modified Registers: 
